'''Mia Amor Mottley''' (n. [[1 di òktober]] [[1965]]) ta un abogado i politiko [[Barbados|barbadiano]]. E ta lider di [[Partido Laboral di Barbados]] (BLP) desde 2008 i [[promé minister]] di [[Barbados]] desde 2018. Mottley ta e promé muhé den e kargonan aki den historia di Barbados.<ref name="Mia">{{citeer web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190108100811/http://www.caribbeanelections.com/knowledge/biography/bios/mottley_mia.asp|titel=Mia Amor Mottley|werk=CaribbeanElections|datum=|bezochtdatum=2022-03-07}}</ref> E ta ademas e promé minister-presidente di e pais bou di su sistema republikano, ku mediante e kambionan konstitushonal introdusi a abolí e monarkia konstitushonal entrante promé di novèmber 2021.

Na 2022 Mottley ta wòrdu inkluí den ''Time's 100 most influential people list'' di e revista merikano Time.<ref>{{citeer web|url=https://today.caricom.org/2022/05/23/pm-mottley-on-times-100-most-influential-people-list/|taal=en|titel=PM Mottley on Time's 100 most influential people list|werk=TodayCaricom.org|datum=23 mei 2022|bezochtdatum=30 mei 2022}}</ref> 

